title: I Think I’ve Been Summoned to Another World and I’m Being Called a Hero, but I’m Just an Ordinary Girl, Aren’t I? - Novel Updates
tags: Female Protagonist   Love Interest Falls in Love First   Transported to Another World   Weak Protagonist
author: イカ墨
description:
A female college student comes back from walking her dog to find herself taken to a cosplay venue… no, it’s Another World!

She’s called a “Hero” but she’s just an ordinary girl, isn’t she? But being a “Hero” means she must have some special abilities! Why wouldn’t she give it her all?

A wacky fantasy comedy with GL included.
>
